\n6. Token ID 8945\n7. Token ID 8946\n8. Token ID 8947\n9. Token ID 8943\n10. Token ID 8942\n11. Token ID 8941\n\nShould a proposal for distribution be initiated before the bears are returned to his wallet, thus leaving him unable to vote on that proposal and secure a distribution on that proposal, if successful, then this proposal shall deem those bears to be in his wallet prior to the initiation of such a proposal so that he can benefit from the outcome of the proposal should that other ultimately end in a distribution. This will mean that if there is a successful distribution proposal, then 11 bears shall be added to the voting numbers for that other proposal in the final calculation amount.  For example, if a distribution proposal is successful with 800 bears voting, then it shall be deemed to be 811 bears should this proposal pass. Further, any snapshot taken prior to the bears being returned to 21xhr shall be deemed to include his bears in that snapshot. He will therefore benefit from any distribution proposal in line with the terms of that other distribution proposal. \n \n\nRATIONALE ‌\n\nThe reasons for this proposal are:\n\n1. Correcting and unfair disadvantage to 21xhr\n2. Reverting 21xhr to the position he was in prior to the creation of the unfair disadvantage\n\n\nTECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS\n\nThe multi-signers will handle the transfer of the 11 bears back to 21xhr as per the terms of this proposal\n\n\nTEST CASES\n\nThere has been a transfer of NFTs from the honeypot to other wallets actioned by multi-signers.\n\n\nCOPYRIGHT ‌\n\nCopyright and related rights waived via CC0.",
