ecification ‌ \n\nThe ownership transfer of the Discord server will be executed through the Discord admin settings. The current server owner, @defijesus will transfer ownership to @21xHR. \n\nThe new ownership will be confirmed by @21xHR upon receipt of the transfer request. \n\n\n\n## Copyright  \n\nCopyright and related rights waived via CC0.",
