      "content": "### BIP Draft: BBH DAO Treasury Distribution\n\n**Author(s):** EdG24  \n**Created:** August 30, 2024  \n**Implementation:** Effective upon BIP approval  \n\n---\n\n#### BUZZED SUMMARY\nThis proposal outlines the plan to distribute the main DAO’s treasury, known as the “honeypot,” to all BBH holders.\n\n#### ABSTRACT\nThe proposal suggests converting the DAO’s Liquid NFTs and cryptocurrencies into ETH and distributing this ETH to all BBH holders, including non-voting, passive, and inactive holders via an airdrop. After the distribution, the BBH DAO will be dissolved, and the BBH NFT collection will continue as a standalone Profile Picture (PFP) collection with no DAO affiliation.\n\n#### MOTIVATION\nThe goal is to provide immediate Fair Value to all holders while ensuring that passive participants are not excluded.\n\n#### SPECIFICATION\n\n- **Communication:** Notifications will be sent via Discord and X (formerly Twitter) upon proposal approval.\n- **Voting Period:** Voting will be open until September 30, 2024 23:59 UTC. Active engagement will occur through communication channels.\n- **Treasury Management:** The BBH DAO will handle costs related to asset consolidation, NFT sales, transaction fees, and airdrop fees. All cryptocurrencies will be converted to ETH before distribution.\n- **Consolidation Period:** October 1, 2024 - October 4 2024\n- **Airdrop Date:** October 10, 2024\n\n#### RATIONALE\n\n- **Inclusiveness:** Comprehensive notifications across all social media channels.\n- **Efficiency:** Possible use of a Layer 2 solution for fund distribution if necessary.\n- **Transparency:** Regular updates and progress reports will be provided.\n- **Snapshot:** Taken on the day the proposal goes to vote.\n\n#### TECHNICAL SPECIFICATION\n\n**Asset Consolidation**\n\n- **NFTs:**\n  - **CrypToadz by Gremplin:** 4 NFTs, Floor Price (FP): 0.466 ETH  \n    - Offers: 1 at 0.47 ETH, 3 at 0.37 ETH\n  - **ON1 Force:** 5 NFTs, Floor Price (FP): 0.2127 ETH  \n    - Offer: 1 at 0.17 ETH\n  - **The Sandbox Lands:** 9 NFTs, Floor Price (FP): 0.0885 ETH  \n    - Offer: 1 at 0.05 ETH\n  - **Treeverse Plots:** 3 NFTs, Floor Price (FP): 0.2399 ETH  \n    - Offer: 1 at 0.21 ETH\n  - **World of Women:** 1 NFT, Floor Price (FP): 0.365 ETH  \n    - Offer: 1 at 0.35 ETH\n  - **Timeless Characters:** 3 NFTs, Floor Price (FP): 0.1149 ETH  \n    - Offers: 1 at 0.60 ETH, 2 at 0.08 ETH\n  - **Mfers:** 1 NFT, Floor Price (FP): 0.2698 ETH  \n    - Offer: 1 at 0.27 ETH\n  - **Decentraland:** 2 NFTs, Floor Price (FP): 0.0999 ETH  \n    - Offer: 1 at 0.08 ETH\n  - **MatrixWorld LandVoucher:** 2 NFTs, Floor Price (FP): 0.1758 ETH  \n    - Offer: 1 at 0.08 ETH\n  - **MetaHero: Generative Identities:** 2 NFTs, Floor Price (FP): 0.087 ETH  \n    - Offer: 1 at 0.07 ETH\n  - **CyberKongz VX:** 1 NFT, Floor Price (FP): 0.09 ETH  \n    - Offer: 1 at 0.05 ETH\n  - **Boss Beauties:** 2 NFTs, Floor Price (FP): 0.034 ETH  \n    - Offer: 1 at 0.02 ETH\n\n**Unstaking and Consolidating Cryptocurrencies**\n\n- Multisignature members will convert various cryptocurrencies (OHM, SAFE, MVI, icETH, LYXe, DAI, INDEX, MANA, and WETH) into Ether (ETH) following proposal approval.\n\n**Distribution Process**\n\n- ETH will be distributed based on voting results. Multisignature members will ensure fair allocation according to the outcome.\n\n**Fair Value Calculation (FVC)**\n\n- The total consolidated value (TCV) will be divided by 9867 BBH NFTs (excluding 100 free-minted BBHs and 29 BBHs in the DAO Treasury).\n\nFV = TCV / 9867 BBH \n\n- Holders will receive FV multiplied by the number of BBH NFTs they hold as of the snapshot.\n\n#### EXAMPLE CALCULATION\n\nIf the proposal is approved, here’s how the distribution will work:\n\n- **Fair Value:** 0.01 ETH per BBH NFT\n  - **Holder A (voted for distribution, owns 20 BBH NFTs):**  \n    - Airdrop Amount: 0.2 ETH  \n    - Calculation: 20 NFTs × 0.01 ETH per NFT\n\n  - **Holder B (did not vote, owns 75 BBH NFTs):**  \n    - Airdrop Amount: 0.75 ETH  \n    - Calculation: 75 NFTs × 0.01 ETH per NFT\n\n  - **Holder C (voted against distribution, owns 96 BBH NFTs):**  \n    - Airdrop Amount: 0.96 ETH  \n    - Calculation: 96 NFTs × 0.01 ETH per NFT\n\n---",
