articipation. \n\n*SUGGESTIONS are not required to be fulfilled by the NFT Flipping Committee.\n\nRationale ‌  \nThe reasons for this proposal are : \nThe NFT Flipping Committee needs leaders\n \nCopyright ‌  \nCopyright and related rights waived via CC0. \n",
